      {
        "id": "mood_analyzer",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Analyze the emotional arc of this song so we can design its music video.\n\nTRANSCRIBED LYRICS\n{{ transcription }}\n\nGENRE: {{ genre }}\nTARGET VISUAL STYLE: {{ style }}\n\nDescribe, in 3-4 vivid sentences:\n1. The dominant mood and how it shifts from opening to end.\n2. The energy level and pacing (calm, building, driving, euphoric...).\n3. A palette of colors, textures, and recurring motifs that match the sound.\n\nWrite it as concrete creative direction a visual artist can act on. No preamble, no headings."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": 740,
            "y": 282
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 280,
          "title": "Build mood-analysis request",
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {
          "transcription": "Drifting through the night, lights blur into color, we rise on the wave of sound",
          "genre": "electronic ambient",
          "style": "abstract geometric patterns, neon colors, flowing energy"
        },
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "mood_analysis",
        "type": "nodetool.agents.Agent",
        "data": {
          "model": {
            "type": "language_model",
            "provider": "openai",
            "id": "gpt-5-mini",
            "name": "GPT-5 mini",
            "path": null,
            "supported_tasks": []
          },
          "system": "You are an award-winning music-video creative director. You translate how a song feels into concrete visual language — mood, energy, color, and motion. Answer with tight, evocative direction only; never restate or acknowledge the request, and never add headings or lists unless asked."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
