        "id": "frame_prompt_generator",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "You are writing image-generation prompts for the frames of a music video.\n\nMOOD & VISUAL DIRECTION\n{{ analysis }}\n\nGENRE: {{ genre }}\nVISUAL STYLE: {{ style }}\n\nWrite exactly {{ count }} image prompts, one per frame, that together trace the song's emotional arc from opening to climax. Each prompt must:\n- be a single self-contained sentence describing one striking frame\n- carry the mood, palette, and motifs from the direction above\n- vary composition and intensity across the sequence (earlier frames calmer, later frames more intense)\n- stay in the \"{{ style }}\" aesthetic\n- contain no lyrics, letters, captions, logos, or watermarks\n\nReturn one prompt per item."
